{"word":"G4434 - πτωχός - ptōchós - pto-khos' - Beggar","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πτωχός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ptōchós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pto-khos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beggar</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"எளிமையுள்ள, தரித்திரரான, ஏழைகளான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. reduced to beggary, begging, mendicant, asking alms"},{"paragraph":"2. poor, needy"},{"paragraph":"3. universally, lacking in anything"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03C9;</b> <b>pto&#x0304;sso&#x0304;</b> (to <i>crouch</i>; akin to <a href=\"#/G4422 - πτοέω - ptoéō - pto-eh'-o/4422\">G4422</a> and the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>); a <i>beggar</i> (as <i>cringing</i>), that is, <i>pauper</i> (strictly denoting absolute or public <i>mendicancy</i>, although also used in a qualified or relative sense; whereas <a href=\"#/G3993 - πένης - pénēs - pen'-ace/3993\">G3993</a> properly means only <i>straitened</i> circumstances in private), literally (often as noun) or figuratively (<i>distressed</i>): - beggar (-ly), poor.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4431/4431\">G4431</a>, <a href=\"#/G4432/4432\">G4432</a>, <a href=\"#/G4433/4433\">G4433</a>, <a href=\"#/G4434/4434\">G4434</a>"}]}